{"tid":1310278,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"《想一想》（Imagine 廣東話試譯）- 潘源良","createTime":"2019-07-12T14:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T15:01:19.000Z","uid":194161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"115efca691b7a951fc73076a20323f50bbd0fefa","tid":1310278,"uid":194161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:58:42.000Z","msg":"潘SAN為社會而寫，希望我地唔係只係發緊夢<br />\n<br />\n得九唔搭八版，唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://song.17sing.tw/uc/song/5733808_1562942820.mp3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsong.17sing.tw%2Fuc%2Fsong%2F5733808_1562942820.mp3&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BYbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=7c6ab9f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://song.17sing.tw/uc/song/5733808_1562942820.mp3</a><br />\n<br />\n試試看 想一想<br />\n這世界 會變樣<br />\n冇國界 冇邊疆<br />\n有勇氣 有盼望<br />\n沒有預設的天堂<br />\n力量 在這方<br />\nAhah...ah...<br />\n<br />\n試試看 想一想<br />\n這世界 會變樣<br />\n抹去痛苦悲傷<br />\n愛與笑 可分享<br />\n放棄暴劫不傷亡<br />\n盡力 為理想<br />\nWoo... woo...<br />\n<br />\n據說是尋夢的我<br />\n天真可笑與無助<br />\n但世上無盡的我<br />\n你也可再加一個<br />\n<br />\n我與你 一起想<br />\n這世界 會變樣<br />\n過去了 可擔當<br />\n再去創 新思想<br />\n愛上現況的當下<br />\n命運 共構想<br />\nWoo... woo...<br />\n<br />\n據說是尋夢的我<br />\n天真可笑與無助<br />\n但世上無盡的我<br />\n你也可再加一個<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%80%E6%83%B3-imagine-%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E8%A9%B1%E8%A9%A6%E8%AD%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%2583%25B3%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2583%25B3-imagine-%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E8%25AD%25AF%2F&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BYbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=4a88f59e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%2583%25B3%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2583%25B3-imagine-%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E8%25AD%25AF%2F&h=40c694b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%